Commentary Text: Krunal Pandya to Markram, out Bowled!! That's not beginner's luck for sure. Pitches, turns and the off-pole is lying flat on the deck. Markram pauses a little before realizing he is gone for a golden duck. That was a tossed up delivery, Markram didn't cover the line and looked to drive. The ball turned past the willow and turned enough to crash into the off-stick. Krunal has his third. Markram b Krunal Pandya 0(1)

Commentary Text: Krunal Pandya to Anmolpreet Singh, out Lbw!! End of a decent knock I would reckon as batting hasn't been easy on this track. That was a flatter one, angled in and Anmolpreet Singh missed the tuck. The ball hit the back pad and was going on to clip the sticks. The onfield call was out and hence the original call stood. Important strike for LSG. Anmolpreet Singh lbw b Krunal Pandya 31(26) [4s-3 6s-1]

Commentary Text: Adil Rashid to Rahul, out Lbw!! That must be out. Yes the finger goes up. But there's a review from Rahul.
